101
00:16:15,320 --> 00:16:19,199
Suntem gata să comandăm !

102
00:16:25,200 --> 00:16:29,113
La ce te uiţi ?

103
00:16:30,920 --> 00:16:34,000
Poţi comanda !

104
00:16:34,000 --> 00:16:35,320
Vreau supă de rechin.

105
00:16:35,320 --> 00:16:37,800
Grozav...

106
00:16:37,800 --> 00:16:39,800
Picioare de broască prăjite..

107
00:16:39,800 --> 00:16:41,400
Buunnnn...

108
00:16:41,400 --> 00:16:43,400
