128
00:17:37,400 --> 00:17:39,520
Merge super cu ardei iute.

129
00:17:39,520 --> 00:17:41,800
Şi asta, porc cu vermicelli din Nordest.

130
00:17:41,800 --> 00:17:45,400
Miroase bine, nu e aşa ?

131
00:17:45,400 --> 00:17:46,600
Ginger...

132
00:17:46,600 --> 00:17:47,399
Exact !

133
00:17:47,400 --> 00:17:49,200
Aromă de ginger

134
00:17:49,200 --> 00:17:51,800
Este special făcută de tatăl meu.

135
00:17:51,800 --> 00:17:52,519
Gândeşte-te la asta.

136
00:17:52,520 --> 00:17:54,600
Porc, vermicelli, şi peşte.

137
00:17:54,600 --> 00:17:56,200
Astea sunt toate alimentele care îţi trebuiesc !

138
00:17:56,200 --> 00:17:57,920
Împreună cu ginger

139
00:17:57,920 --> 00:17:58,799
